Hindi ba pwedeng tanggapin mo na lang
na maaaring isang tao lang

441
00:35:41.890 --> 00:35:43.016
sino bang hindi ka mahal?

442
00:35:45.310 --> 00:35:48.981
Hindi lang... isang tao.

443
00:35:49.064 --> 00:35:51.567
Geez, sino pa bang may ayaw sayo?

444
00:35:58.782 --> 00:35:59.658
Ako?

445
00:36:03.453 --> 00:36:04.288
Hey.

446
00:36:05.330 --> 00:36:08.125
Sa tingin mo ba ay dumating ako
lahat ng paraan dito upang bayaran ang aking pananatili?

447
00:36:10.627 --> 00:36:14.172
