at tawagan siya ulit.

499
00:40:19.126 --> 00:40:20.001
Mabuti.

500
00:40:20.794 --> 00:40:23.255
Puntahan mo siya ng madalas simula ngayon, okay?

501
00:40:25.173 --> 00:40:26.007
hindi ko gagawin.

502
00:40:27.425 --> 00:40:28.510
Bakit hindi?

503
00:40:29.970 --> 00:40:30.804
Masyadong malayo.

504
00:40:31.388 --> 00:40:32.931
Hindi naman masyadong malayo.

505
00:40:33.014 --> 00:40:35.267
Sabihin mo lang kung kailan.
Dadalhin kita doon anumang oras.

506
00:40:35.350 --> 00:40:37.227
Hindi talaga ito bagay sa akin.

507
00:40:37.310 --> 00:40:39.396
I just tried the gnocchi out of curiosity.

508
00:40:40.021 --> 00:40:43.191
Mas gusto ko ang maanghang,
parang <i>gaengsigi </i>sinigang.

509
00:40:50.615 --> 00:40:51.575
Mayroon ka pa?

510
00:40:51.658 --> 00:40:52.576
Syempre!

511
00:40:52.659 --> 00:40:55.203
Kumuha ako ng sariwang bean sprouts
sa palengke

512
00:40:55.287 --> 00:40:56.955
at nagluto ng isang malaking kaldero.

513
00:40:58.373 --> 00:40:59.541
Sige.

514
00:41:12.929 --> 00:41:14.806
- Tiyo.
- Ano?

515
00:41:15.473 --> 00:41:17.559
Lalabas ako ngayon kasama si Se-jin.

516
00:41:19.311 --> 00:41:20.520
Sa totoo lang?

517
00:41:20.604 --> 00:41:23.231
May nararamdaman din pala siya para sa akin.

518
00:41:23.315 --> 00:41:24.816
Hey.

519
00:41:24.900 --> 00:41:26.902
Binabati kita, Han-gyul.

520
00:41:26.985 --> 00:41:28.653
Sino kaya ang hindi magkakagusto sayo?

521
