<i>Talagang si Sun Jae-gyu iyon.</i>

727
00:59:47.459 --> 00:59:49.169
{\an8}Jae-gyu. Ay naku!

728
00:59:50.337 --> 00:59:51.297
{\an8}Bakit ka nandito, Nanay?

729
00:59:51.380 --> 00:59:52.798
{\an8}- May anak ka na.
